"{\"uid\": \"rnz.co.nz-news-sport-524745-olympics-2024-paris-gold-has-special-taste-for-khelif-after-gender-dispute\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByAadi Nair,Reuters  Gold medallist Algeria's Imane Khelif poses on the podium during the medal ceremony for the women's 66kg final boxing category during the Paris 2024 Olympic Games at the Roland-Garros Stadium, in Paris on 9 August 2024.Photo:MAURO PIMENTEL / AFP  Victory at the Paris Olympics has \\\"a special taste\\\", said Algeria's Imane Khelif after winning boxing gold on Friday, following two weeks of speculation over her eligibility amid a gender dispute that has engulfed the Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nair\", \"score\": 0.9999929687764315, \"rank\": 7.031273007507716e-06, \"text\": \"Nair\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nair\"}, {\"begin\": 12, \"end\": 19, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.999999999975671, \"rank\": 2.3398026296414824e-11, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9962568245103113, \"rank\": 0.0037572373748218472, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 217, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998922249, \"rank\": 1.0783051402941482e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9962568245103113, \"rank\": 0.0037572373748218472, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif,who beat China's Yang Liu to claim the welterweight title,and Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting were caught up in a storm that has dominated headlines and been the subject of heated debate on social media platforms.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9935760651538824, \"rank\": 0.002842052936640545, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834678135, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\"}, {\"begin\": 563, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.999220753518821, \"rank\": 0.0005554028588345432, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both were disqualified by the International Boxing Association (IBA) from the 2023 World Championships, which said a sex chromosome test had ruled both of them ineligible.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.857302255340769e-25, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.6680496022395166, \"rank\": 0.495930420513573, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are competing in the Olympics after the International Olympic Committee (IOC)stripped the IBA of its status as the sport's governing body in 2023and took control of organising the boxing in Paris.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 923, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.6680496022395166, \"rank\": 0.495930420513573, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998922249, \"rank\": 1.0783051402941482e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At these Games, the IOC is using boxing eligibility rules that were applied at the 2016 and 2021 Olympics which do not include gender testing.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4542849448702386e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a woman like any woman,\\\" Khelif told a news conference after her gold medal.\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was born a woman and I have lived as a woman but there are enemies to success and they can can not digest my success.\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That also gives my success a special taste.\\\"\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Algeria's Imane Khelif reacts after beating China's Yang Liu in the women's 66kg final boxing match to win the gold medal during the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.Photo:Mauro Pimentel / AFP  The IOC rejected the results of the IBA-ordered tests on Khelif and Lin as arbitrary and illegitimate, saying there was no reason to conduct them.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9962568245103113, \"rank\": 0.0037572373748218472, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9935760651538824, \"rank\": 0.002842052936640545, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1528, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834678135, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\"}, {\"begin\": 1666, \"end\": 1669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4542849448702386e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif, a silver medallist at the 2022 worlds, said she did not understand the IBA's actions.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1889, \"end\": 1892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.6680496022395166, \"rank\": 0.495930420513573, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All that is being said about me on social media is immoral.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to change the minds of people around the world,\\\" Khelif added.\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 2035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From 2018, I competed under the authority of the IBA and they know everything about me.\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2087, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.6680496022395166, \"rank\": 0.495930420513573, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not recognise this IBA.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.6680496022395166, \"rank\": 0.495930420513573, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the members hate me and I do not know why.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I sent them a message today that my honour is above everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif is the first Algerian woman to win an Olympic boxing gold medal, as well as the first Algerian boxer to win gold since Hocine Soltani at the 1996 Olympics in Atlanta.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9874685794025863, \"rank\": 0.012690243075787158, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2367, \"end\": 2375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9874685794025863, \"rank\": 0.012690243075787158, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hocine_Soltani\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hocine Soltani\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hocine_Soltani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hocine_Soltani\"}, {\"begin\": 2439, \"end\": 2446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999686133383, \"rank\": 2.0615311031189867e-08, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old has had immense support from the crowds at her fights, with Algerian fans, many of whom are women, flocking to Roland Garros and the North Paris Arena to cheer her on.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2525, \"end\": 2533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9874685794025863, \"rank\": 0.012690243075787158, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2576, \"end\": 2589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.5766318235741351, \"rank\": 0.7342088293930654, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 2604, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998922249, \"rank\": 1.0783051402941482e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Algerian woman is known for her courage,\\\" Khelif said.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2639, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9874685794025863, \"rank\": 0.012690243075787158, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The coming of these women to the stadium sent a message to the world that our honour is above everything.\\\"\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"-Reuters  Copyright \\u00a92024,Radio New Zealand  The female boxer was thrust into the centre of a gender dispute at the Paris Games, but has had the last say.\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2830, \"end\": 2847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.9994215708876634, \"rank\": 0.0005787638861576949, \"text\": \"Radio New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif is one of Algerias top boxers.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane has identifed as a female since birth, lived her whole life as a womam, including her sports career.\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a Unicefambassador she has been a champion for\\u2026Audio  Many sportswomen who appear too powerful, too successful, or look \\\"too masculine\\\" according to a particular set of values are at risk of being targeted, academics say.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gender row: International Olympic Committee says Algerian boxer Imane Khelif and Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting were being targeted.\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3349, \"end\": 3380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3386, \"end\": 3394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9874685794025863, \"rank\": 0.012690243075787158, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 3401, \"end\": 3413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 3418, \"end\": 3424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.999220753518821, \"rank\": 0.0005554028588345432, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 3427, \"end\": 3438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r